  a linear combination of <m>\vvec_1</m> and
  <m>\vvec_2</m>. </p></li>

  <li><p> If <m>\coords{\xvec}{\bcal} = \twovec{-3}{5}</m>, find
  <m>\coords{A\xvec}{\bcal}</m>. </p></li>
      </ol></p>
      </statement>

